Class HwmfMisc.WmfSetBkMode

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.poi.hwmf.record.HwmfMisc.WmfSetBkMode
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    GenericRecord, HwmfRecord
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    HemfMisc.EmfSetBkMode
    Enclosing class:
    HwmfMisc 

    public static class HwmfMisc.WmfSetBkMode
extends java.lang.Object
implements HwmfRecord
    The META_SETBKMODE record defines the background raster operation mix mode in the playback device context. The background mix mode is the mode for combining pens, text, hatched brushes, and interiors of filled objects with background colors on the output surface.(Meta_SETBKMED记录定义播放设备上下文中的背景格栅操作混合模式。背景混合模式是将笔、文本、阴影画笔和填充对象的内部与输出表面上的背景颜色结合起来的模式。)
